('CAT003', 'Phrases', 'French speaking by phrases is for French speaking beginners who need help to understand the basic of speaking French. this section will use very simple phrases and expressions to help you with your French speaking.', 'images/talking.jpg'),
('CAT004', 'Love To Know', 'Let''s know french even more ...', 'images/lovetoknow.jpg');
